is off the table?

891
00:36:50,285 --> 00:36:52,120
It was never on the table.

892
00:36:52,187 --> 00:36:53,588
- What's this?
- A press release.

893
00:36:53,656 --> 00:36:56,190
"Female head of major law firm

894
00:36:56,258 --> 00:36:57,579
