It's no big deal.

986
00:41:29,264 --> 00:41:30,665
How did it go down?

987
00:41:30,732 --> 00:41:32,700
Did you tell him if he puts
one of ours in the hospital,

988
00:41:32,768 --> 00:41:34,468
