996
00:41:50,252 --> 00:41:52,186
Two doors down,
they're doing <i>Steel Magnolias.</i>

997
00:41:52,254 --> 00:41:53,754
You'd fit right in.

998
00:41:53,822 --> 00:41:55,756
I'm more
of a <i>Beaches</i> man myself.

999
00:41:55,824 --> 00:41:57,591
