1003
00:42:03,031 --> 00:42:05,199
so I decided to farm out
the case.

1004
00:42:05,267 --> 00:42:07,668
Whose ass
are we gonna kick now?

1005
00:42:07,736 --> 00:42:10,638
Actually,
an old classmate of mine.

1006
00:42:10,706 --> 00:42:13,174
Let me guess...

1007
00:42:13,241 --> 00:42:16,010
Daniel Hardman.